{"tid":545460,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫學]食完arcoxia之後每餐後都胃痛","createTime":"2018-01-30T13:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T19:00:18.000Z","uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e7e98b622e4c8ec8cac0c19b8f53fd2f3b1072","tid":545460,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"上個星期腳痛去咗睇醫生<br />\n佢開咗7粒90mg 嘅arcoxia配埋7粒40mg嘅pantoprazole<br />\n比我食 一日一粒<br />\n食到今日開始 每餐完咗個胃就乸住乸住痛<br />\n究竟關唔關隻藥太重事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇話arcoxia會搞到stomach ulcer<br />\n有冇讀醫嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65637592ade87b326e206f5eee339e6f17b9bcf5","tid":545460,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4782890fc956009d1ea29e82b8a3d3d18e60a3dc","tid":545460,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"arcoxia 我食完無痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議你食左飯先"},{"pid":"188bb3387db1a482e6dde536cee15a17104a7abb","tid":545460,"uid":87644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T23:29:10.000Z","msg":"可以試下食完飯之後先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過你食咁短時間應該都唔會係 ulcer 最多只係 GI upset姐<br />\n其實腳痛用下gel 都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035fa008b86a7db53377f43443af862d24cf0517","tid":545460,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"因為強酸性，乸胃"},{"pid":"75f18dc6d7d2d7773197aeee922418c7cf1c82e3","tid":545460,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0